org.neo4j.cypherdsl.core

  • Packages that use org.neo4j.cypherdsl.core 
    Package Description
    org.neo4j.cypherdsl.core
    Contains an internal DSL for creating Cypher.
    org.neo4j.cypherdsl.core.renderer
    A renderer for statements in the simplest form possible.
